						<div class="postbody">It looks to me like you room data is still full screen even though the HUD is covering it. Start designing the rooms shorter. And you might want to compress your data. This is just from loading room 1. Look at all those 01's. It will save alot of ROM space to compress this and load it somewhere in the RAM as collision info.</div>

					
